      "acceptanceCriteria": "Competing turbulence and hemolysis constitutive models compared quantitatively; model-form uncertainty bounded at Gradation 5.",
      "rationale": "Single turbulence model (SST k-omega) and single hemolysis power-law model used without comparison to alternatives. Model-form uncertainty is entirely uncharacterized. Achieved level 1."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
